      "blocks": [
        {
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "data": {
            "html": "<h2>Overview</h2><p>Project management fundamentals serve as the cornerstone for successful project execution. These principles guide project managers through every stage of a project, from initiation to completion.</p><p>Think of managing a project like planning a journey — each step below maps a key concept to something familiar:</p><h2>1. Understanding the Basics</h2><p>First, you need to grasp what project management is all about. Think of it as learning the language of project management — the terms, concepts, and principles that form the foundation of every successful project.</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0,
            "gridY": 0,
            "gridW": 12,
            "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "data": {
            "html": "<h2>2. Planning Like a Pro</h2><p>Next, you'll learn how to plan your journey. This involves:</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0,
            "gridY": 1,
            "gridW": 12,
            "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              {
                "html": "<p>Setting clear goals</p>"
              },
              {
                "html": "<p>Making a timeline</p>"
              },
              {
                "html": "<p>Figuring out what resources you'll need along the way</p>"
              }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0,
            "gridY": 2,
            "gridW": 12,
            "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "data": {
            "html": "<h2>3. Putting Plans into Action</h2><p>Once your plan is ready, it's time to hit the road! This involves:</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0,
            "gridY": 3,
            "gridW": 12,
            "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "orderIndex": 4,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              {
                "html": "<p>Coordinating tasks</p>"
              },
              {
                "html": "<p>Assigning roles to team members</p>"
              },
              {
                "html": "<p>Ensuring everyone knows what they're doing</p>"
              }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0,
            "gridY": 4,
            "gridW": 12,
            "gridH": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
